My first css map, you are able to cut the power to the warehouse. Cts spawn outside, Ts spawn inside - a little like cs_assault

__

This is my first map and I am aware of one glitch with the hostages - they don't follow you out of one of the doors, if anyone can help It would be greatly appreciated

I have since noticed a few glitches and Chizbone shed light on some too so I'm fixing those at the moment.

I put heaps of effort into this map - I hope you enjoy it
